imesofisrael.com%2Fjeffrey-rosen-trumps-new-talmud-quoting-acting-attorney-general%2Famp%2F&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7nxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=366a1e91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.timesofisrael.com/jeffrey-rosen-trumps-new-talmud-quoting-acting-attorney-general/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\nJeffrey Rosen, Trump&rsquo;s new Talmud-quoting acting attorney general<br />\nRosen, who had no experience in Justice Department or as a prosecutor when appointed, will take over for last few weeks of Trump administration after William Barr resigns"},{"pid":"458f6454fdb67583d46e34c2967afcc91acbfcc2","tid":2325942,"uid":258696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"Trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a40f37c0a9fe44557e02b6b9e0f693e2d5afd1","tid":2325942,"uid":324629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"458f6454fdb67583d46e34c2967afcc91acbfcc2","tid":2325942,"uid":258696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"Trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c067c48a82872a0ddb0f18a40fe4789cf50620db","tid":2325942,"uid":26708,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ea960c9770a2be61ac3ab9aafa7279c94c9daa7","tid":2325942,"uid":26708,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:06:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.timesofisrael.com/jeffrey-rosen-trumps-new-talmud-quoting-acting-attorney-general/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fjeffrey-rosen-trumps-new-talmud-quoting-acting-attorney-general%2Famp%2F&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7nxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=366a1e91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.timesofisrael.com/jeffrey-rosen-trumps-new-talmud-quoting-acting-attorney-general/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\nJeffrey Rosen, Trump&rsquo;s new Talmud-quoting acting attorney general<br />\nRosen, who had no experience in Justice Department or as a prosecutor when appointed, will take over for last few weeks of Trump administration after William Barr resigns"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"Speaking just weeks ago about combating anti-Semitism, Jeffrey Adam Rosen, the deputy attorney general, quoted Rabbi Tarfon: &ldquo;<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">It is not incumbent on you to complete the work, but neither can you desist from doing it.</span></span></strong>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nNow Rosen is set to become a historical footnote by completing William Barr&rsquo;s work as attorney general. Barr quit Monday, and US President Donald Trump said on Twitter that Rosen would be acting attorney general."},{"pid":"2a9359ff57b97c034cf82ad3a303f6dbc204d91f","tid":2325942,"uid":26708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"Rosen, who is <span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"large\">Jewish</span></strong></span>, delivered remarks in October at a State Department conference on anti-Semitism. He said that &ldquo;addressing this disturbing rise of anti-Semitism is a priority of the Justice Department,&rdquo; but also cautioned that it was incumbent on law enforcement to respect speech freedoms. He took exception particularly to the term &ldquo;hate speech&rdquo;, which is favored by a number of anti-defamation groups, including major Jewish organizations. Trump frequently has been accused of peddling &ldquo;hate speech.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;At least in the realm of the law, we should look to find a better term than &lsquo;hate speech&rsquo;, as that term can cover some things that are protected by the First Amendment and some that are not, so it has not proven very useful,&rdquo; Rosen said. &ldquo;And sometimes the term &lsquo;hate speech&rsquo; has been used to label whatever the person using the phrase doesn&rsquo;t like. It has become too easy to label political speech as such."},{"pid":"4fcc56fb3986820402810c741eb275ed958b54e5","tid":2325942,"uid":78732,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"Arrest all the traitors!"},{"pid":"5babaece20684fd5c1848453d4d29c84f74e4389","tid":2325942,"uid":51840,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LLinWood/status/1338623862486020096?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLLinWood%2Fstatus%2F1338623862486020096%3Fs%3D19&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7nxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=6ecd02f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLLinWood%2Fstatus%2F1338623862486020096%3Fs%3D19&h=fa9e5174\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LLinWood/status/1338623862486020096?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"f1f841f614548f9bca56cd23837e27f3c8f2be4c","tid":2325942,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5babaece20684fd5c1848453d4d29c84f74e4389","tid":2325942,"uid":51840,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LLinWood/status/1338623862486020096?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLLinWood%2Fstatus%2F1338623862486020096%3Fs%3D19&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7nxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=6ecd02f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLLinWood%2Fstatus%2F1338623862486020096%3Fs%3D19&h=fa9e5174\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LLinWood/status/1338623862486020096?s=19</a>"},"citedBy":0