82 and became a partner in 1988.  He was elected to that firm&rsquo;s global management committee in 1999.  After his public-service appointments during 2003-2009, Mr. Rosen returned to Kirkland &amp; Ellis LLP as a partner from 2009-2017.  Throughout his years in private practice, Mr. Rosen handled complex litigation across the United States, including jury trials, bench evidentiary hearings, arbitrations, and appellate arguments.  Among his wide-ranging litigation practice were cases involving antitrust, securities, <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>RICO</strong></span></span>, business torts, trade secrets, contracts, government enforcement actions, and product liability, including class actions, as well as regulatory matters."},{"pid":"0b8bf320689f289ec51cde8c90de48b86969fe73","tid":2325942,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"係咪真係搵到證據 dominion 有行賄巴爾？"},{"pid":"0832fc00aee71254048bf051cf4682a59a451c05","tid":2325942,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b12d59fa3189a2fab9e855243e5b76948fa4bf3c","tid":2325942,"uid":1900,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:18:48.000Z","msg":"羅森係82空降師出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"會唔會用軍方渠道去查舞弊案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408bce08e7bc54ccfa427963cd227e56c0a90e12","tid":2325942,"uid":261913,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"0b8bf320689f289ec51cde8c90de48b86969fe73","tid":2325942,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"係咪真係搵到證據 dominion 有行賄巴爾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"我估多少係搵到佢痛腳啦<br />\n唔係點會唔出聲就肯走"},{"pid":"25bc6ea226f55163dbfa5578757faed18c5213c3","tid":2325942,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:39:37.